verse.name: v1
verse.lines:
Prince of Peace,
Counselor,
Merciful,
Son of God.

verse.name: v2
verse.lines:
Lord of Host,
Conqueror,
Coming King and
Everliving God.

verse.name: c1
verse.lines:
I extol You,
Lord I extol You,
You are high above the earth,
All creation shouts Your worth.

verse.name: c2
verse.lines:
I extol You,
Lord I extol You,
My Jehovah, I extol You.
